### ============================================
### 4.4 LESSONS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### GET /v1/lessons/:lessonId
### Obtener información de una lección
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/lessons/:lessonId/question
### Obtener siguiente pregunta disponible
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/question
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================

### POST /v1/lessons/:lessonId/answer
### Registrar respuesta del usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "{{questionId}}",
  "selectedOptionId": "{{answerId}}",
  "timeSpentSeconds": 25
}

@attemptId = {{response.body.data.attemptId}}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/lessons/:lessonId/progress
### Obtener progreso del usuario en lección
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ERROR CASES
### ============================================

### POST /v1/lessons/:lessonId/answer - Time out of range
POST {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "{{questionId}}",
  "selectedOptionId": "{{answerId}}",
  "timeSpentSeconds": 5000
}

### ============================================

### POST /v1/lessons/:lessonId/answer - Invalid UUID
POST {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "not-a-uuid",
  "selectedOptionId": "{{answerId}}",
  "timeSpentSeconds": 25
}

### ============================================

### GET /v1/lessons/:lessonId - Lesson not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
